c: 64
v: 12
t: "watyeu allah -ayha alnas- wanqadu 'iilayh fima 'amr bih wanahaa enh, wa'atieuu alrasul salaa allah ealayh wslm, fima bllaghkm bih ean rbh, fa'iina 'aeradtum ean taeat allah wrswlh, falays ealaa rasulina darar fi 'ieradkm, wa'iinama ealayh 'an yblghkm ma 'ursil bih blaghana wadih albyan"